issue.title: Initial WebSocket Functionality
issue.body:
- Create scaffolding for websockets (i.e., 2-way client-server communication)
- Initial implementations for join room, leave room, upvote, and downvote
- Merry Christmas

comment.body:
This is a fatty, but if any, I'd like some feedback on the general model for how I'm handling MessageTypes here given that we can't _truly_ route with websockets. 

Two places to check this out are:
-  `websocketHandler` in `concertRouter.js`
- `WebsocketClient` in `WebsocketUtils.js`
